Class CollisionChainingDatastructure

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.yrck.datastructures.CollisionChainingDatastructure
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MyDatastructure 

    public class CollisionChainingDatastructure
extends java.lang.Object
implements MyDatastructure
    Implementation of a Collision Chainging hashtable.

    Collision chaining works by using linked lists when a collision of hashes occurs.

    Author:
    Yorick de Boer
